name: flowers #6
description:
There is a place where everything goes
the colorful sunsets    
the laughter with friends
the reflective insomnia

                                
there's a place where everything goes
the kisses across the street 
the hands tangled in the train
the memories that hurt

there is a place where everything goes
childhood afternoons
the mended hearts
the anguish, the confinements

there is a place where everything goes that crosses us

there is a place that is our history
and that makes us what we are.
